flowchart LR
  customer[Person: Customer / Driver] --> web[Container: Web application\nAngular]
  subgraph ParcelFlow[Software system: ParcelFlow]
    web -->|HTTPS/JSON| api[Container: Delivery API\nJava / Spring Boot]
    api --> db[(Container: Delivery database\nPostgreSQL)]
    db --> relay[Container: Outbox relay\nJava worker]
    relay --> broker{{Container: Event broker\nKafka}}
    broker --> billing[Container: Billing worker\nJava worker]
    broker --> notification[Container: Notification worker\nJava worker]
  end
  api --> carrier[External system: Carrier API]
  api --> payment[External system: Payment provider]
